<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Hi Albert=2C<o:p></o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp=3B</o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">You never need to apologise for complaining=2C becau=
se there=92s=0A=
an exceptionally high likelihood that I=92ll do the same in the next letter=
. And=0A=
I feel today is one such day!<o:p></o:p></p>=0A=
