ain=0A=
at bay. And so it goes=2C these valiant attempts to quell pain only to see =
it=0A=
rear its head again a short time later.<o:p></o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp=3B</o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I=92ll start with a few everyday things before I sta=
