:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp=3B</o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Alright=2C back to doom=2C gloom and disillusionment=
. <o:p></o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I have referred to my recent interest in Watts and R=
