to=0A=
create our own meaning within the meaninglessness=2C which is no easy feat.=
<o:p></o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">This is why the concept of value is so interesting t=
o me. If=0A=
you start from the premise that everything is meaningless and valueless=2C =
then=0A=
it is very interesting to see the way that humans manipulate things to give=
=0A=
