=0A=
Happiness comes to those who are most able to disillusion themselves! How=
=0A=
wonderful it must feel to be on a mission towards what you value.<o:p></o:p=
></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Watts spoke a little bit about the world as a drama =
=96 he=0A=
called it the game of white verse black. To take an example=2C there are so=
me=0A=
