=92s a=0A=
constant battle between these two groups. They=92re both occupied=2C this =
=91quest=92=0A=
gives their life meaning =96 everybody wins!<o:p></o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp=3B</o:p></p>=0A=
=0A=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I=92ve never had a cause like this that I=92ve been =
motivated to=0A=
